{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6b362273ce","title":"讽刺诗一首","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第一集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d7c5ce5bfa","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"6b362273ce"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0d6384de3f","name":"李冶"},{"id":"fa51fe5561","name":"西南美术专科学校"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a3c10219fd","type":"title","text":"讽刺诗一首","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"c12e134748","type":"authors","text":"西南美术专科学校李冶","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"22cdf4d8b2","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：李冶，男，西南美术专科学校附中教员，解放前当过伪军，伪警察，加入过三青团。现为青年团员，一贯对党不满，散布了许多反党反社会主义言论。这些言论大都是他平时讲的，未包括在他的文章中，故摘录如后：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"50e73aa053","type":"paragraph","text":"①仇恨党。他说“党员都是乌七八糟，我在市委统战部，十三中和西师遇到的，就没有一个好人”“你们这些共产党员只跟着党走，没有一点脑筋”“大学里的党员领导，都是些饭桶，我看只有华岗才算个有学问的人，那些批评他的人，简直是胡说”“我把共产党恨入骨髓”，“共产党吹嘘成绩，报上有些报导翻来复去地表功，看起来真肉麻。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"123a2b6112","type":"paragraph","text":"②谩骂毛主席。他在疗养院疗养时，重庆日报发表了毛主席的旧体诗。他征求护士的意见，护士说有些看不懂。他说“当然嘛！狗屁不通，你怎么看得懂”，并打电话质问重庆日报：“毛主席的诗有错误，你们为什么要发表？”他还对附中的学生说“毛主席的东西看不得，共产党没有真正有本事的人”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"c8948df35e","type":"paragraph","text":"③崇拜资产阶级民主。他说“现在共产党比国民党还要专制”“我们的经济制度好，而政治制度却没有美国民主，美国人可以批评艾森豪威尔，而我们敢批评毛泽东吗？”“印度在政治上就比我们民主”“马列主义不见得永久是真理，你看现在报上就有人在反对了。我常常在想：难道就没有比社会主义更优越，更适合中国国情的政治制度吗？”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"38b489fac1","type":"paragraph","text":"在这首诗里，李冶极其恶毒地谩骂党的干部，把他们诬蔑成为一些不学无术，只凭“裙带关系”，才当上领导的人。]","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"a68e033f04","type":"paragraph","text":"有这样一位报考历史学科副博士研究生","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"66a49e0d0f","type":"paragraph","text":"试卷问他：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"7de378775b","type":"paragraph","text":"“李白何人？”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"3577a5fbd7","type":"paragraph","text":"他回答：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"007f33fe2a","type":"paragraph","text":"“李宗仁、白崇禧”。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"60c07021de","type":"paragraph","text":"试卷问他：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"14c3f44543","type":"paragraph","text":"“寇准是谁？”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"217deade67","type":"paragraph","text":"他回答：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"78e5e602e3","type":"paragraph","text":"“是汉朝一位宰相”。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"f0b720a1b1","type":"paragraph","text":"看他的成绩，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"2ac49c94a0","type":"paragraph","text":"实在有点可怜相，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"b85f134a83","type":"paragraph","text":"而他却当上了“历史专家”！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"f0c0dfc439","type":"paragraph","text":"你说为啥？","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"d91725d2fa","type":"paragraph","text":"因为：","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"0e7d62f6e9","type":"paragraph","text":"“他姐夫是司长”。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"bb09475a1d","type":"paragraph","text":"*　　*　　*","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"cb556b2819","type":"paragraph","text":"有这样一位大学系主任","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"58994bc59c","type":"paragraph","text":"英文","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"a3fcc6d714","type":"paragraph","text":"不懂A．B．C，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"941a3e8198","type":"paragraph","text":"日文","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"bbe63eaf47","type":"paragraph","text":"不懂アレフラ","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"e064992139","type":"paragraph","text":"俄语字母倒顺认不清，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"9ed830f610","type":"paragraph","text":"而他却当上了俄语系主任，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"ea8d98c8e9","type":"paragraph","text":"你说为啥？","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"e32b442141","type":"paragraph","text":"因为：","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"716036a5c3","type":"paragraph","text":"“他丈夫是院长”。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"f5ce6801a5","type":"paragraph","text":"*　　*　　*","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"eeceb12edf","type":"paragraph","text":"“朋友，你感觉这种情况怎样？”","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"b19ac8e039","type":"paragraph","text":"“这又有什么稀奇，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"e3cb362c2d","type":"paragraph","text":"普天之下皆系王土","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"1ffda96d6f","type":"paragraph","text":"这是自古以来的真理”。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"55152c7e8e","type":"paragraph","text":"“唉，我总算还有一个希望，","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"72160efb07","type":"paragraph","text":"盼望我的女儿快快长，","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"73776ad19f","type":"paragraph","text":"长大了，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"50c7f03a46","type":"paragraph","text":"嫁给共产党员部长，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"3c9f95422e","type":"paragraph","text":"这样，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"ee5bf130ea","type":"paragraph","text":"我总也可以当上一位教授专家！”","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"},{"id":"9bb4af5608","type":"paragraph","text":" 57．5月间鸣放初期。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce"}],"page":{"id":"f732adb843","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6b362273ce","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}